\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n什麼空拉麵"},{"pid":"a5af4c6fe3befe8f9f204dc7d6f4c23ccdfdc0b7","tid":1903810,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e4ccf18e3cff9682e47dd876d4929a1f1c7442","tid":1903810,"uid":145782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"小弟繼續獻醜啦 歡迎大家比下意見或者想屌鳩我嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望喺我有生之日同大家分享浪遊嘅喜悅x唏噓感 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係悶架<br />\n白羊男係一冇盤就屌曬鬼喊曬鬼咁<br />\n我真係好唔捨得佢 亦都感覺到做人好撚無謂 賺錢賺錢然後洗錢又交際又要顧屋企 真心呢個circle好辛苦 有冇巴絲諗過 活到咁長命有乜撚意義 冇意思呀係！<br />\n唉 總之<br />\n人其實跟本就與生俱來係個個體，乜都係靠自己生存空間走落去</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1999</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寫埋Day 4-5啦屌</span><br />\n<br />\n嚟到札幌 緊係要食<strong>湯咖哩</strong>啦<br />\n第一次食日式湯咖喱原來係咁多材料<br />\n呢間簿野區嘅SHO-RIN <br />\n有雞又多菜仲要係超級嫩雞 正過死臭雞 去激安又發現有紙箱人Domdom 幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GnTBmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GnTBmK.jpg&h=740619fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wn83YAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWn83YAf.jpg&h=daac7d76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xac8qfp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXac8qfp.jpg&h=c54ef111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>二夅市場</ins><br />\n聽講喺日本真係要試吓魚生食早餐，所以札幌出名嘅海鮮wet market，其實間間都差唔多而且收得幾貴，所以我是但食咗間平平哋嘅seto算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvMMWVN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvMMWVN.jpg&h=6f149163&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQgQD9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQgQD9d.jpg&h=512566c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>狸小路 - OM二手古著</ins><br />\n頂，咁都比我揾到North Face背心 實在太興奮，呢度要鳴謝下杜如窿，係佢喺北海道攻略度介紹過嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SPiNO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SPiNO5.jpg&h=bfe900fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7snsF9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7snsF9e.jpg&h=b3056eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>北海道大學</ins><br />\n好有西方建築嘅mix，喺度影幾張相扮返大學生都幾好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9W5sUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9W5sUk.jpg&h=4bbd4a10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMScSk4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMScSk4.jpg&h=b40c97d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJje5Gn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJje5Gn.jpg&h=7f46f962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>羊之丘展望台</ins><br />\n好似係北海道大學創辦人嘅克拉克博士，手指著講Boys,&nbsp;Be&nbsp;Ambitious! 個景望到半個札幌市，本身早幾個星期應該有玩滑雪板，不過依家完左，又係冇乜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJtvD1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJtvD1N.jpg&h=fb99608b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZrw7Vk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZrw7Vk.jpg&h=df329398&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRaemfq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRaemfq.jpg&h=81bf861a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚飯都係湯咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />スープカレー奥芝商店<br />\n呢間係超級濃郁嘅鮮蝦湯底，好撚正呀媽！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOOzmfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOOzmfL.jpg&h=2171eb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>北海道神宮</ins><br />\n抽到韱 - 末吉，就嚟玩撚完 - 完！ （達哥把聲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQOC3uS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQOC3uS.jpg&h=fbd746f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNz6WPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNz6WPU.jpg&h=6aed81b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>定山溪溫泉</ins><br />\n獨撚一個浸溫泉都係第一次，不過戶外望住雪景浸個溫泉係幾正，足足玩左兩個鐘，沖完之後即刻用滴露，有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6Aemhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6Aemhn.jpg&h=a2124fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tUB1LJ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtUB1LJ9.jpg&h=d2dc97b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yC4JvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yC4JvV.jpg&h=9c8383f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行街 - APIA/ESTA/JR TOWER<br />\n比小弟我揾到嚟日本想買嘅converse，香港冇得賣，日本限定呀！仲要有得tax-free，唔買對唔住自己<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXjF1ih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXjF1ih.jpg&h=9f820ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢到嘅Starbucks杯全部都係Sakura(突然想唱 &ldquo;Sakura~ Sakura~齊來張開腿屌下~&rdquo;)最岩送比啲女神豬扒。不過都幾貴下，換咗三張free drink返嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfbUmiN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfbUmiN.jpg&h=1d03ee8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw，我必須要重申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺日本屙屎完全係一大人生享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟今次着膠囊旅館，不過係有得企喺度比較豪華小小嘅膠囊，真係靜過圖書館，超級局有冇得調節個暖氣，連打飛機都唔可以咁大聲，不過勝在呢間旅館幾新，而且樓下係錢湯澡堂咁樣沖涼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17pVQc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17pVQc5.jpg&h=533961f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"有無hostel個名可以share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" c