.cx/i/9SPiNO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SPiNO5.jpg&h=bfe900fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7snsF9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7snsF9e.jpg&h=b3056eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>北海道大學</ins><br />\n好有西方建築嘅mix，喺度影幾張相扮返大學生都幾好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9W5sUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9W5sUk.jpg&h=4bbd4a10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMScSk4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMScSk4.jpg&h=b40c97d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJje5Gn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJje5Gn.jpg&h=7f46f962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>羊之丘展望台</ins><br />\n好似係北海道大學創辦人嘅克拉克博士，手指著講Boys,&nbsp;Be&nbsp;Ambitious! 個景望到半個札幌市，本身早幾個星期應該有玩滑雪板，不過依家完左，又係冇乜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJtvD1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJtvD1N.jpg&h=fb99608b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZrw7Vk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZrw7Vk.jpg&h=df329398&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRaemfq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRaemfq.jpg&h=81bf861a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚飯都係湯咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />スープカレー奥芝商店<br />\n呢間係超級濃郁嘅鮮蝦湯底，好撚正呀媽！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOOzmfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOOzmfL.jpg&h=2171eb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>北海道神宮</ins><br />\n抽到韱 - 末吉，就嚟玩撚完 - 完！ （達哥把聲）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQOC3uS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQOC3uS.jpg&h=fbd746f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"